# Build context for cmd/brain/Dockerfile is the repo root. Keep it lean and —
# critically — never copy dev state (which can hold instance .env secrets) into
# the build context.
.git
.dev
web-ui
**/node_modules
**/*.tar
*.test
dev/test-qemu/mkosi.extra
dev/test-qemu/mkosi.pkgmngr
dev/test-qemu/mkosi.tools
